en die Mobilitätswende, der Online-Handel, die Vernetzung in Sozialen Medien, Big Data, Künstliche Intelligenz, Mixed Reality u.a.m in dieser dritten Auflage einen erweiterten Fokus. Das Buch unterstützt die Lehre und Forschung sowie die Unternehmenspraxis.  aThis book provides comprehensive insights into the spectrum of digital information, communication and reservation systems, and their intersections with tourism and travel, and also addresses current developments in digital tourism. Case studies based on practice and processes round out the explanations.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aAngewandte Informatik. 4aDigitaler Tourismus. 4aMobilitätsmanagement. 4aReiseverkehrsmanagement. 4aTourismusmanagement. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Industries / Hospitality, Travel & Tourism.2bisacsh1 aGoecke, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoecke, Robert, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKurz, Eberhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKurz, Eberhard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchulz, Axel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWeithöner, Uwe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeithöner, Uwe, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG OWV ebook Paket Lehrbücher Wirtschaftswiss. 2022z9783110994674oZDB-23-OLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2022z9783110992922oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831107124900 cprintz978311069039240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311078686640uhttps://www.degruyter.com